Author: bumbumboleji
Text: I think it’s super sweet you care about your friend, there’s a huge range on the spectrum of disorders and some people just don’t like eating very much   Also stupid websites and magazines give people tips like “drink iced water lol” so it’s not weird per se for someone to have picked that info up  If you are worried just talk to your friend nicely about it  In a non confrontational way, again I think it’s super nice of you to care
